basic.Peptide Name: Br-AFP2 (natural AMPs; defensins; plants; XXQ, UCSS1a; 4S=S)
basic.Source: Brassica rapa subsp. chinensis; Brassica napus
basic.Target Organism: low salt medium A: active against A. brassicola (IC50 75 ug/ml), B.cinerea (IC50 >100 ug/ml), F. culmorum (IC50 38 ug/ml), F. oxysporum f.sp. lycopersici (IC50 42 ug/ml), P. oryzae (IC50 3 ug/ml), and V. dahliae (IC50 15 ug/ml). Activity and Seq updated 2/2023.
